Double Sided Adhesive Tape Market Overview
The global double-sided adhesive tape market was valued at USD 12.5 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 18.7 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.8% during the forecast period. This growth is driven by increasing applications across industries such as construction, automotive, and electronics. Double-sided adhesive tapes offer superior bonding, reducing the need for traditional mechanical fasteners, thus becoming essential in lightweight manufacturing.

The market is characterized by evolving consumer preferences, technological advancements, and the rise of sustainable adhesive solutions. Companies are focusing on eco-friendly tapes that meet stringent regulations, further fueling market demand. Download a sample for an in-depth understanding of the industry trends, competitive landscape, and market segmentation.

